    {
      "id": "reference-view-unification-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Reference / View Unification",
      "position": {
        "x": 81.16666666666652,
        "y": -1015
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Reference / View Unification\n\nThe destination is not one flat species. What we actually seem to have is a small family with primitive poles and one obvious hybrid.\n\n- `PortNode` = minimal reference primitive\n- `DynamicViewNode` = minimal hosted-view primitive\n- `GraphReferenceNode` = hybrid of both, plus embedded graph runtime\n- `Bridge` = mode on the minimal reference primitive for now",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
