        "x": 937.8333333333333,
        "y": 75
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Shared Base Shape\n\nLikely shared across the family:\n- explicit target or host target\n- declared surface choice\n- action/traversal mode\n- optional boundary manifestation\n- shared chrome / theme-state behavior\n- semantic zoom participation\n\nThis is a family resemblance model, not proof that every member is the same primitive.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
