      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Embedded Graph Runtime Shell",
      "position": {
        "x": 2598.8333333333335,
        "y": 395
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Embedded Graph Runtime Shell\n\nThe real extra thing `GraphReferenceNode` currently owns is not autorun selection policy. It is:\n- embedded graph surface\n- iframe/embed lifecycle\n- expansion policy\n- traversal/open behavior\n\nThat suggests a better split:\n- shared family surface\n- optional embedded-graph behavior package",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
