    {
      "id": "reference-view-unification-note-view-implementation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "View Implementation Difference",
      "position": {
        "x": 2137.8333333333335,
        "y": 88.33333333333326
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# View Implementation Difference\n\n`PortNode` and `GraphReferenceNode` may still belong to the same underlying family even when they render through different view technologies.\n\nExamples:\n- compact div-style reference surface\n- live iframe embed surface\n\nIframe vs div is a view implementation difference, not automatically a node-species difference.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
